{{> layout/header}}
<link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/information.css">
<main class="cc-main">
    <div class="cc-container cc-info-page">
        <section class="cc-info-hero cc-info-hero--open">
            <div>
                <p class="cc-info-hero__eyebrow">TICKET OPEN CALENDAR</p>
                <h1>오픈 예정</h1>
                <p>놓치고 싶지 않은 공연의 티켓 오픈 일정을 미리 확인하세요.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="cc-info-hero__icon" aria-hidden="true">
                <svg viewBox="0 0 64 64" fill="none">
                    <rect x="10" y="13" width="44" height="41" rx="10"/>
                    <path d="M20 8v11M44 8v11M10 25h44"/>
                    <path d="m25 39 5 5 11-13"/>
                </svg>
            </div>
        </section>

        <section class="cc-info-section">
            <div class="cc-info-section__head">
                <div>
                    <p class="cc-info-kicker">다가오는 티켓 오픈</p>
                    <h2>이번 주 오픈 일정</h2>
                </div>

                <div class="cc-info-filter" id="genre-filter">
                    <button type="button" data-genre="all">전체</button>
                    <button type="button" data-genre="concert">콘서트</button>
                    <button type="button" data-genre="musical">뮤지컬</button>
                    <button type="button" data-genre="festival">페스티벌</button>
                    <button type="button" data-genre="fanmeeting">팬미팅</button>
                    <button type="button" data-genre="classic">클래식</button>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="concert-container">
                <div class="concert-list" style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 20px;">

                    {{#openSoonList}}
                        <article class="cc-card cc-list-card cc-open-soon-card" style="display: flex; flex-direction: row; align-items: center; padding: 16px; border-bottom: 1px solid #eee;">

                            <a class="cc-list-card__poster" href="/concerts/{{id}}" style="flex-shrink: 0; width: 140px; margin-right: 24px;">
                                <img src="{{posterUrl}}" alt="{{title}} 포스터" style="width: 100%; height: auto; border-radius: 8px; box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);">
                            </a>

                            <div class="cc-list-card__body" style="flex-grow: 1; display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 6px;">
                    <span class="cc-concert-card__category" style="font-size: 13px; color: #888;">
                        {{#genreLabel}}{{genreLabel}}{{/genreLabel}}{{^genreLabel}}콘서트{{/genreLabel}}
                    </span>

                                <h3 class="cc-list-card__title" style="margin: 0; font-size: 1.3rem;">
                                    <a href="/concerts/{{id}}" style="text-decoration: none; color: #333;">{{title}}</a>
                                </h3>

                                <p class="cc-list-card__line cc-open-date" style="color: var(--cc-main-color, #ff4081); font-weight: bold; margin: 4px 0 8px 0; font-size: 1.1rem;">
                                    🔔 오픈일: {{ticketOpenDate}}
                                </p>

                                <p class="cc-list-card__line" style="margin: 0; color: #555;">{{venueName}}</p>
                                <p class="cc-list-card__line" style="margin: 0; color: #888; font-size: 0.9rem;">{{address}}</p>
                            </div>

                            <button class="cc-heart" type="button" data-concert-id="{{id}}" aria-label="관심 공연 등록" aria-pressed="false" style="align-self: flex-start; margin-left: 16px; background: none; border: none; cursor: pointer;">
                                <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" width="20" height="20"><path d="M20.84 4.61a5.5 5.5 0 0 0-7.78 0L12 5.67l-1.06-1.06a5.5 5.5 0 0 0-7.78 7.78l1.06 1.06L12 21.23l7.78-7.78 1.06-1.06a5.5 5.5 0 0 0 0-7.78z"/></svg>
                            </button>

                        </article>
                    {{/openSoonList}}

                    {{^openSoonList}}
                        <div class="no-data" style="text-align: center; padding: 50px;">
                            <p>현재 오픈 예정인 정보가 없습니다. 😭</p>
                        </div>
                    {{/openSoonList}}

                </div>
            </div>
        </section>
    </div>
</main>
<script>window.OPEN_SOON_DATA = { currentGenre: "{{currentGenre}}" };</script>
<script src="/js/concert/open-soon.js"></script>
{{> layout/footer}}
